* copy* 
/runner_tmp
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/dist/
frontend/.matrixlab-frontend.pid
frontend/.matrixlab-frontend.log
# Match the pidfile / log wherever the Makefile lands them — some
# operators run `make` from the project root, others from frontend/.
.matrixlab-frontend.pid
.matrixlab-frontend.log
# Python build metadata regenerated on every ``pip install -e .``
# or ``python -m build``.  The directory name follows
# ``[project].name`` from pyproject.toml; we renamed the PyPI
# distribution from ``matrixlab`` to ``agent-matrix-lab``, so use a
# glob to catch the current name plus any future rename.
*.egg-info/
# uv lockfile — matrixlab uses setuptools, not uv, as its primary
# package manager.  uv.lock can appear as a side effect of
# contributors running ``uv run`` for ad-hoc builds; ignore it so
# only ``pyproject.toml`` is the source of truth for deps.
uv.lock
# Build outputs from ``python -m build``.
/dist/
/build/
*.whl
*.tar.gz
/runner_envs
/runner_state
